# Fumapress Content

- Every doc page needs frontmatter with at least `title`; add `description` for SEO and OG images.
- Folder URLs: `content/guide/index.mdx` maps to `/guide`.
- Optional sidebar: `meta.json` or `meta.yaml` per folder (`title`, `pages`, `root`, `icon`, …).
- Link to [blit386 engine docs on GitHub](https://github.com/blit386/blit386/tree/main/docs) for API reference; summarize
  here, do not copy full API tables.
- No emoji in content or UI strings.
- After editing links, run `pnpm run docs:links`.
